=== Cliff/gradient interpretation ===
  - CLIFF at t_lat=2: large drop nf=1→nf=5, smaller after
    → position-IDs at t>0 or LPE indexing
  - GRADIENT: monotonic drop across all t_lat values
    → sequence-length effect (mask growth / attention dilution)
